			<div class="date"><small>May</small><br />17</div>
			
			<h2><a href="http://lifehackery.com/2008/05/17/50-amazingly-helpful-time-tested-tips-for-the-kitchen/" title="50 Amazingly Helpful Time-Tested Tips for the Kitchen">50 Amazingly Helpful Time-Tested Tips for the Kitchen</a><br>
			<small class="author_byline" id="author_byline">by <a href="http://lifehackery.com/author/lifehackery/" title="Posts by lifehackery">lifehackery</a>&nbsp;-&nbsp;<a href="/?author_name=lifehackery">All Posts By This Author</a></small> <br><br>
			</h2>
			
			
			<div class="social"><div class="left"><a href="#comments" class="comments">163 Comments</a>
<a href="?print=1" class="print">Print This</a>
<a href="?email=1" class="email">Send To Friend</a>
<a target="_blank" title="Bookmark using any bookmark manager!" onclick="window.open('http://www.addthis.com/bookmark.php?pub=&amp;url=http//lifehackery.com/2008/05/17/50-amazingly-helpful-time-tested-tips-for-the-kitchen&amp;title=', 'addthis', 'scrollbars=yes,menubar=no,width=620,height=520,resizable=yes,toolbar=no,location=no,status=no'); return false;" href="http://www.addthis.com/bookmark.php" class="addthis">Bookmark...</a></div><div id="post-ratings-372" class="post-ratings"><img id="rating_372_1" src="http://lifehackery.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-postratings/images/stars/rating_on.gif" alt="1 Star" title="1 Star" onmouseover="current_rating(372, 1, '1 Star');" onmouseout="ratings_off(4, 5);" onclick="rate_post();" onkeypress="rate_post();" style="cursor: pointer; border: 0px;" /><img id="rating_372_2" src="http://lifehackery.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-postratings/images/stars/rating_on.gif" alt="2 Stars" title="2 Stars" onmouseover="current_rating(372, 2, '2 Stars');" onmouseout="ratings_off(4, 5);" onclick="rate_post();" onkeypress="rate_post();" style="cursor: pointer; border: 0px;" /><img id="rating_372_3" src="http://lifehackery.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-postratings/images/stars/rating_on.gif" alt="3 Stars" title="3 Stars" onmouseover="current_rating(372, 3, '3 Stars');" onmouseout="ratings_off(4, 5);" onclick="rate_post();" onkeypress="rate_post();" style="cursor: pointer; border: 0px;" /><img id="rating_372_4" src="http://lifehackery.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-postratings/images/stars/rating_on.gif" alt="4 Stars" title="4 Stars" onmouseover="current_rating(372, 4, '4 Stars');" onmouseout="ratings_off(4, 5);" onclick="rate_post();" onkeypress="rate_post();" style="cursor: pointer; border: 0px;" /><img id="rating_372_5" src="http://lifehackery.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-postratings/images/stars/rating_half.gif" alt="5 Stars" title="5 Stars" onmouseover="current_rating(372, 5, '5 Stars');" onmouseout="ratings_off(4, 5);" onclick="rate_post();" onkeypress="rat