          	      		          	<p>#31 is likewise an old wives tale, and can seriously aggravate any burns.  As a trained EMT who has seen many cases of people following such kitchen lore, I understand that these myths are popular - but for your own sake!  Slease, please do not put mustard, butter, or anything else on a wound, other than to run it under cold water if it is a burn.</p>
