      <div class='commenttext'>
        <div class="commentp">
          	      		          	<p>just a further comment:  I enjoyed the list.  Very cute.  But a word of warning as the EMT said:  salves ointments or in this case mustard applied to a burn will actually make the injury worse because it will seal in the heat and prolong the burning process.  Additionally,  broken skin that may occur,  will obsorb mustard and whatever else is shmeared on, increasing the chance of infection.  Flushing continuously ( read as:  Longer then you think is needed!  Like 15 mins)  with cool water for superficial burns,  and dial. 911 for more serious burns!</p>
      		        </div>
</div>
