Also, if you keep your house plants clean (i.e. dusting and wiping to keep off said nasty cooties) there really shouldn&#8217;t be much to be worried about.  As long as the wound is kept clean I don&#8217;t see any problems.<br />
If plant juices are so terrible why is it recommended that we eat several servings of fruits and vegetables everyday to maintain a healthy body?</p>
      		        </div>
</div>
